Evolution Outcome

Evolution Cycle 1 transformed the KYBBA Framework from a collection of Entity Type Categories into a structured architectural system based on Structural Roles and System Capacities.

This established the first stable architectural foundation for future Evolution Cycles and created a consistent methodology for continuing framework development.

